page.screenshot(new Page.ScreenshotOptions().setPath(Paths.get("ArrowLeft.png")));
page.keyboard().press("Shift+O");
page.screenshot(new Page.ScreenshotOptions().setPath(Paths.get("O.png")));
browser.close();
```

